features: LASTS ALL YEAR. GUARANTEED! Guarantee is valid for one year from purchase date. Does not cover misuse.
Scan, study and organize your notes with the Five Star App. Create instant flashcards and sync your notes to Google Drive to access them anywhere from any device.

Rearrange the movable plastic dividers anywhere in your notebook to organize notes. Dividers with expanding pockets hold 8-1/2" x 11" handouts. Visible tabs from front cover make it easy to flip to any section.

body.description: LASTS ALL YEAR. GUARANTEED!* This Five Star 1 subject notebook has 100 double-sided, college ruled sheets, which fight ink bleed. A 2-pocket divider holds 11" x 8 1/2" sheets, while tough pockets help prevent tears. Notebook also has water resistant covers. Neat Sheet perforated sheets make it easy to tear out assignments. Spiral Lock wire binding prevents coil snags on your clothes or in your backpack. Sheets measure 11" x 8 1/2" when torn out. Overall notebook size is 11" x 9 3/4". 6 pack includes: Dark Gray, Bright Orange, Lime, Yellow, Teal and Bright Pink. *Guarantee is valid for one year from purchase date. Does not cover misuse.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Built Strong to Last Long Gear up for a strong year with Five Star notebooks, folders, binders and more. We strive to provide high-quality, durable products to empower students to succeed throughout the school year. While school can be challenging and stressful at times, with the right tools, you can take on anything. Five Star Spiral Notebooks Rely on Five Star notebooks to keep up with your busy day! These notebooks work just as hard as you do with ink bleed resistant paper, reinforced pockets and water-resistant covers. And the features don’t stop there. Spiral Lock wire keeps the coil from snagging your clothes or backpack, and Neat Sheet perforated pages easily tear out with clean edges. When you have to take notes, write an essay or turn in an important assignment, Five Star has you covered. High-quality paper resists ink bleed** Tear-resistant 2-pocket dividers*** Water-resistant plastic front cover Heavy duty, water-resistant paper board back cover Spiral Lock wire prevents coil snags

Five Star Spiral Notebooks Stronger Pockets Reinforced storage pockets help prevent tears.*** Notes and hand-outs stay neat and organized. Durable & Water-Resistant This notebook is made with a water-resistant plastic front cover and heavy duty paper board back cover so it can stand up to daily wear and tear. High-Quality Paper College ruled, 15 lb. paper resists ink bleed.** Ideal for notetaking and homework, you can write on both sides of the paper and notes will stay clear and legible. **Under normal usage, paper resists ink bleed with common student writing instruments such as pencils, ball point pens, gel pens, felt tip pens and highlighters. Spiral Lock Spiral Lock wire prevents coil snags so it won’t get caught on your clothes or backpack. The Neat Sheet perforated pages easily tear out with clean edges.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I used these for school and loved how I never had to buy anynire notebooks for the rest of college I was set! I love the colors and how many you get in this set. Great deal!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 21, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I got the assorted colors pack of six notebooks and received the correct colors and brand. I've been using them in college to take notes in (I know, I'm old school for not using a laptop or ipad.. but I just remember things better when I actually write them down) and they're pretty sturdy. Even though they're called one subject, I used some of them for two semesters. Never had a problem with them falling apart or anything, and while my pens would often ghost through the paper, I don't think they ever bled through.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 31, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very happy with my purchase!
reviews.reviewText: I'm a long-term user of 5-star notebooks. They are by far my favorite to write in. The durability, pocketed folders, & fun colors make taking notes way more enjoyable for me.After I already make the purchase for these notebooks, I read that a large number of customers were given wrong colors or even received completely different brands... Yeah, I for sure should have checked the reviews before I buying them, but figured it would be hard to not like these notebooks.Anywho, I was VERY happy to receive the correct brand & colors! I will definitely be buying again!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 12, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very sturdy, pages stay put until you are ready to remove them!
reviews.reviewText: Great value for the cost!! Not just for students in school. I bought these for myself and they are wonderful to keep you organized, journaling if you choose, and just great to have when needed. Very sturdy, some on the market are weak/flimsy but not these!! Love the inside pocket and the vivid colors!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 8, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best one subject notebook for high school
reviews.reviewText: Perforated better than some other brands so you can pull out pages without tearing the paper. Please take note that there's a new style of Five Star notebook that says "Study guide" included. These types look virtually the same as the classic ones I am reviewing. However, pages have a triangle next to each line that apparently has some electronic way to then load the page online. That might be cool but at this time my student only wants to write notes on a notebook piece of paper that doesn't have triangles to make it look busy and not then load those notes online. She of course can still take a photo of her notes and send them electronically without triangles.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 28, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These are good notebooks for high school! I received the correct colors I ordered. Very durable and thick, I have never had a page fallout that I did not purposefully rip out. My only issue is that the front pocket does not fit a full-size piece of paper, so I would have to fold my papers to fit them in the pocket. Other than that they have been very useful!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 27, 2019
reviews.reviewText: As a highschooler, I used these notebooks throughout my four years and absolutely loved them. The colors were appealing, the cover was strong, and the paper is high quality. 100% would recommend for anyone who plans to do a lot of writing. I even had to use one in the rain a few times, and although the paper was soaked, there was no tearing or ripping except along the perforation and I was able to use that notebook plenty of times after it had dried. Definitely worth the money.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 24, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I’m very picky
reviews.reviewText: I’m very picky about the notebooks and pens I use. My notebooks came in the box gently packed and ready to go. There were no bents (thankfully) and the notebooks have a plastic-ish sturdy covering instead of the prone to rip paper covers. It also comes with a folder on the inside. Nothing fancy more like those cardboard-ish folders but still a plus for extra pages if you need it
